Description:
   Dissolution is an advanced Magi offensive spell that channels raw arcane
   entropy to dissolve the target's physical integrity. The spell projects
   a stream of corrosive arcane energy that breaks down organic and inorganic
   matter at the molecular level, causing severe acid-like damage as the
   target's substance is literally dissolved.

   Dissolution is one of the Magi's high-tier single-target offensive spells,
   offering strong damage with no secondary effects. It is reliable in
   situations where elemental immunities would reduce fire or ice spells'
   effectiveness, as the dissolution energy bypasses conventional elemental
   resistances by attacking the fundamental coherence of matter rather than
   delivering thermal or kinetic force.
